Z","msg":"講真呢d野都唔係班法官自己揸主意，都係睇自己國家頭架啦，大各位五毛唔洗急著出黎放負<br />\n<br />\n（正視聽）不停講all talk no action班仆街唔係放負五毛就係比五毛影響既on9仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2446021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2446021</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"超多5毛入哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7add3e14c13b0cbe58f7700111226c467eaab7","tid":2451550,"uid":107577,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"24438da64cf97c301c6bfe66d35d7a71d0ec5a4e","tid":2451550,"uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"79feca50dabc9c3759e927f6fbeed12b4ebe91a3","tid":2451550,"uid":107577,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"宜家冇違<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>良知？</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"又想放負？收皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"放負？<br />\n有黨安法嘅嗰一刻就應該要走啦<br />\n佢嘅存在係每一秒都為黨安法正名緊<br />\n<br />\n有黨安法仲行到普通法？<br />\n你個body仲未dead？"},{"pid":"687591ef5cd71e0785126e164c6e19f6ec2e9816","tid":2451550,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"應該差唔多會辭職了"},{"pid":"8cfa787abad9e8d84be8afe869a0a02726144d1a","tid":2451550,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"身兼終審法院非常任法官的英國最高法院院長韋彥德，早前據報短期內決定是否繼續擔任終院非常任法官。韋彥德昨在英國國會聽證會上雖未有透露其決定，但明言若香港情況到了他們不能再基於良知做下去，他便不會留任。<br />\n<br />\n韋彥德昨以視像方式出席英國國會聽證會。他在會上稱，會定期與英國外相和司法大臣檢討，自1997年回歸起派英國法官到港的安排。他預期短期內會有下一次會議，表明「當然」會考慮香港不斷變化的局勢，若香港司法獨立被破壞、法庭行為可能違反法治，又或香港局勢變化至不能基於良心做下去，他就不會留任，強調「你可以放心，我不會容許置（英國）最高法院的名聲於險境。（You can be assured that I won&rsquo;t allow the Supreme Court&rsquo;s reputation to be put at risk.）」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/RJ7DPVCZLNECPEGJ6OVBIRLMNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FRJ7DPVCZLNECPEGJ6OVBIRLMNA%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2ebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=1985765f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FRJ7DPVCZLNECPEGJ6OVBIRLMNA%2F&h=592b8b0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/RJ7DPVCZLNECPEGJ6OVBIRLMNA/</a>"},{"pid":"59a66c4b9090b9f708d0496a130d45ee195f420e","tid":2451550,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/britain-should-avoid-undermining-the-hong-kong-judiciary-2j7nmft5d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fbritain-should-avoid-undermining-the-hong-kong-judiciary-2j7nmft5d&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2ebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4b06d9ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/britain-should-avoid-undermining-the-hong-kong-judiciary-2j7nmft5d</a><br />\nLord Sumption篇文仲叫人信香港司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3c653bd4b8e5c9f6f02a606f9c31a733eb5b57","tid":2451550,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"呢個講法姐係班法官準備隨時閃<br />\n係等本國下令<br />\n<br />\n去到呢個敏感時刻,走與唔去應該會問左本國先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA-%E8%A6%81%E8%88%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%81%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F-%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%258C%2584%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%25